Isn't the NTSC color simulation in Nestopia supposed to be pretty accurate? If so, just load one of the several PD ROMs that show all 52(?) colors on-screen at once, tweak the simulated TV knobs to your liking, take a screenshot, then extract each color one-by-one and place them into a new .PAL file. Load into your favorite emulator and enjoy. That's what I did, anyway.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=935">BMF54123</a> — Thu Mar 18, 2010 9:34 pm</p><hr />
